# (Free)RADIUS user and group management API

(Free)RADIUS user and group management API.

# Group Users

Resources related to RADIUS user management.

## User Collection [/api/v1/services/radius/users]

### List All Users [GET]

The "check" and "reply" properties are lists of RADIUS Check and Reply attributes according the
RADIUS specification ([RFC2865](https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc2865)),
as well as
[internal ones](https://github.com/vasilakisfil/secure_file_transfer/blob/46b95a88150e5e9605786ff9301d5259af1a28ab/config/radius-dictionary#L145).

