### Create a New User [POST]

+ Attributes (object)
    + check (object) - Requested RADIUS check attributes
        + User-name (string)
        + Password-Type (string) - "SSHA1-Password", "Cleartest-Password", etc.
        + User-Password (string)
    + reply (object) - Requested RADIUS reply attributes
    + confirm (object)
        + check (object)
            + User-Password(string) 

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            'check' => {
                'User-Name' => "__user_test",
                'Password-Type' => "SSHA1-Password",
                'User-Password'=> "pass"
            },
            'confirm' => {
                'check' => {
                    'User-Password' => "pass"
                }
            }
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /api/v1/services/radius/users/__user_test

